inputs.name: example-subnet-tags-00651520
inputs.templateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-subnet-tags-nodeLaunchConfiguration-999b3f4
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-014876436b45dd370","subnet-0efd6c4c6688a6a88","subnet-0f0534e236acbffbb"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-subnet-tags-eksCluster-69098eb-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-subnet-tags-eksCluster-69098eb
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
